record_data.record_title: Certificate of Concurrence for SFA with NW Ohio IA LLC
record_data.record_plain_text:
CERTIFICATE OF CONCURRENCE
This is to certify that Northwest Ohio Solar, LLC assents to and concurs with the Amended and Restated Northwest Ohio Wind and Solar + Storage Project Shared Facilities Agreement, dated as of November 10, 2022, by and among Northwest Ohio Wind, LLC, Northwest Ohio Solar, LLC, and Northwest Ohio IA, LLC, filed by the designated filing company, Northwest Ohio IA, LLC, as described below and as it may be revised from time to time.
Designated Filing Company (DFC): Northwest Ohio IA, LLC
DFC Tariff Title: Tariffs and Agreements
DFC Tariff Program: Electric MBR
DFC Tariff Record Adopted by Reference: Shared Facilities Agrmt., Amended & Restated SFA with NW Ohio Wind & NW Ohio Solar (refer to Section 2 for Grant of Shared Facilities Rights)
record_data.filing_title: Certificate of Concurrence for Shared Facilities Agreement with Waiver
